Grinding Gears

"Cookie Clicker meets Factorio"

Genre: Idle, incremental

Platform: Desktop

The player is trying to build and improve their ever-expanding factory

Simplistic, text-based UI with minimal sound triggered by special events

A clicker game completely controlled through the mouse

